{"about_the_game":"Swordai is a multiplayer sword fighting game where players compete to climb a tower full of monsters, traps, and treasure.  Swordai combines a fast paced directional combat system that includes ripostes, feints, parries, kicks and combos with massive multiplayer dungeons, loot, abilities and a skill tree.  Enter the tower alone or with friends, battle your way through monsters, bosses and other players, and escape with your loot alive.<br><br>As you progress through the various trials and challenges that Swordai has to offer you will unlock skills and abilities that allow you to customize your combat style as you strive to gain power and reach the top of the tower.  Each floor of the tower is a unique hand-crafted dungeon crawl with a variety of different enemies, trials and monsters as well as the ever present threat of other players.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/Swordai---Steam-Store-Description-header-imagesArtboard-2.png?t=1729871255\" /><br><br>Fight with or against up to 50 other players as you compete to traverse enormous dungeons filled with monsters, bosses, traps, and treasures.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/groupVsCultivator.gif?t=1729871255\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/Swordai---Steam-Store-Description-header-imagesArtboard-5.png?t=1729871255\" /><br><br>Swordai uses an &quot;easy to learn, difficult to master&quot; directional combat system that provides a fluid yet brutal combat experience that will keep you coming back day after to day to hone your skills.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/dueGifNEw.gif?t=1729871255\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/Swordai---Steam-Store-Description-header-imagesArtboard-3.png?t=1729871255\" /><br><br>Slay bosses, find chests, or kill other players within the tower, then find an exit portal to escape with your loot.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/looterGif.gif?t=1729871255\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/Swordai---Steam-Store-Description-header-imagesArtboard-4.png?t=1729871255\" /><br><br>Unlock new powerful abilities and upgrades as you progress.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/extras/skillUnlockGif.gif?t=1729871255\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729871255","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729871255","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729871255","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321890/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729871255","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Swordai is a game centered around sword fighting and melee combat in a dark fantasy setting so there is violence and blood throughout the game."},"detailed_description":"<h1>Ready to duel?</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cl